properties.text:
╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║  FAT MEX — Qwen Edit 2511 Dataset Generator      ║
╠══════════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║                                                  ║
║  PURPOSE: Generate LoRA training images with     ║
║  Qwen Image Edit 2511 using a face reference.    ║
║                                                  ║
║  HOW TO USE:                                     ║
║  1. Load your reference face in LoadImage        ║
║  2. Write your prompt (use 'image 1' to ref)     ║
║  3. Set seed to 'randomize'                      ║
║  4. Queue each prompt to build dataset           ║
║                                                  ║
║  EXAMPLE PROMPTS (one per run):                  ║
║  • Generate the person from image 1 in a         ║
║    portrait photo, neutral expression, white bg   ║
║  • Generate the person from image 1 wearing a    ║
║    red dress, standing pose, studio lighting     ║
║  • Generate the person from image 1 at a cafe,   ║
║    casual outfit, natural light, candid          ║
║  • Generate the person from image 1 in workout   ║
║    clothes, gym setting, dynamic pose            ║
║  • Generate the person from image 1 in formal    ║
║    business attire, office background            ║
║  • Generate the person from image 1 at the       ║
║    beach, swimwear, golden hour, full body       ║
║  • Generate the person from image 1 in winter    ║
║    coat, snowy street, looking at camera         ║
║  • Generate the person from image 1 close-up     ║
║    face shot, slight smile, soft lighting        ║
║  • Generate the person from image 1 from the     ║
║    side, profile view, dramatic lighting         ║
║  • Generate the person from image 1 looking      ║
║    over shoulder, evening dress, city lights     ║
║  • Generate the person from image 1 sitting on   ║
║    a couch, casual loungewear, cozy interior     ║
║  • Generate the person from image 1 in a         ║
║    leather jacket, street style, urban setting   ║
║                                                  ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

info.name: Fat Mex Qwen Edit 2511 Dataset Generator
info.description: Generate LoRA training images using Qwen Image Edit 2511. Load a reference face, write prompts describing different scenes/outfits/poses, and build a training dataset one image at a time.
info.author: Fat Mex
